          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1586949165419-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>mayo</strong> with<strong> half</strong> the <strong>chopped mint</strong>, <strong>half</strong> your <strong>white wine</strong> <strong>vinegar </strong>(you'll use the rest later!), 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> in a small bowl – this is your<strong> minty mayo</strong></p><p>Reboil a kettle</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1586949170397-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1586949170397-x400.jpg",
