          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1586949170397-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1586949170397-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Run the<strong> drained potatoes</strong> under <strong>cold running water</strong> until they're cool enough to handle, then return them to the pot, add a knob of <strong>butter</strong> and crush gently</p><p>Add the <strong>flaked smoked basa </strong>and <strong>sliced spring onion</strong>, season with a generous pinch<strong> </strong>of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and mix gently</p><p>Divide the mix then shape them into 2 fishcakes per person</p><p>Press the <strong>fishcakes</strong> into your <strong>panko breadcrumbs </strong>until evenly coated</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1586949174460-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1586949174460-x400.jpg",
