          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1586949174460-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1586949174460-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1586949174460-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>coated</strong> <strong>fishcakes</strong> to the reserved tray with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> (line the tray with fresh<strong> tin foil</strong>)</p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 15-20 min or until golden and crispy – these are your <strong>smoked basa fishcakes</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>salad </strong>then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
